index 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000..d1be23e647ea1fb19d253bca77ce97434c86a4ea
--- /dev/null
+++ b/packages/blockchain/.review-slices/T13.fix.md
@@ -0,0 +1,29 @@
+# Blockchain test fixes test fixes
+
+**Package:** T13
+**Scope:** packages/blockchain
+
+## Summary
+Updated blockchain tests to stop depending on live Optimism RPC and to assert the corrected fork boundary behavior. Replaced stale RPC fixtures with deterministic local RPC-shaped blocks that preserve json-rpc hash parent relationships used by the delBlock/putBlock fixes. Refreshed affected snapshots after the package version and fixture output changed.
+
+## Tests passing
+all
+
+## Tests still failing
+0
+
+## Changes
+- src/test/getBlocks.ts:10 - Added deterministic mock RPC hashes, RPC block fixtures, and mock transport for blockchain tests.
+- src/test/getBlocks.ts:99 - Rebuilt getMockBlocks from local RPC fixtures while preserving __tevmJsonRpcBlockHash metadata.
+- src/createBaseChain.spec.ts:36 - Switched fork setup from live Optimism transport to the deterministic mock transport.
+- src/actions/getBlock.spec.ts:46 - Switched RPC fetch tests to the deterministic mock transport.
+- src/actions/getBlock.spec.ts:54 - Updated stale newer-than-fork expectation by fetching an older block from a higher fork point.
+- src/actions/getBlockByTag.spec.ts:57 - Switched tag-based fork fetch test to the deterministic mock transport.
+- src/actions/validateHeader.spec.ts:21 - Forked at block 1 so the valid-header test has a fetchable parent block.
+- src/utils/getBlockFromRpc.spec.ts:7 - Reworked RPC tests to use local mock RPC blocks instead of live test-utils transport.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/delBlock.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated error snapshot package version.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/getBlock.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated getBlock snapshots for deterministic fixtures and current package version.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/getBlockByTag.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated getBlockByTag snapshots for deterministic fixtures and current package version.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/getCanonicalHeadBlock.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated error snapshot package version.
+- src/actions/__snapshots__/getIteratorHead.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated iterator-head error snapshots package version.
+- src/utils/__snapshots__/getBlockFromRpc.spec.ts.snap:1 - Updated getBlockFromRpc snapshots for deterministic fixtures and current package version.
